OL,5, The government is setting up a job     
OL,6, centre league table and will give #250 
OL,7, bonuses to staff who get the most      
OL,8, people into work.                      
OL,10,FIt is part of a pilot scheme in 60 job 
OL,11,Fcentres aiming to get more Universal   
OL,12,FCredit claimants into employment.      
OL,14,FThe government said it is right to     
OL,15,Freward staff when they help people     
OL,16,Fsecure work.                           
OL,18,FBut the PCS union said the scheme was  
OL,19,F"gimmicky" and would not help address  
OL,20,Fthe "poverty pay" of job centre staff. 
